<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="405" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="12.[135,1341,1203,1906]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[137,490,1794,1827]" pageId="12" pageNumber="405">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Buchara Shrew has a small distribution that needs to be carefully monitored.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
